title: Spiceklub
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Indian, International, Italian, Fast food
description: Opened summer 2014, a modern Indian vegetarian cuisine restaurant with a molecular menu featuring pav bhaji fondue; deconstructed dahi vada; spinach and cheese cigars; paan mousse; and bubbling kulfi. Has many vegan options.
streetAddress: 8A, Janta Industrial Estate, Opposite Phoenix Mills, Senapati Bapat Road
